{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "加斯特为了完成治疗疾病的“治愈熏香”\\n一直在不断努力。\\n终于……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "哈啊、哈啊……你在这里啊！\\n喂，卢卡！你听着！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "喂喂，你怎么\\n上气不接下气的？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "成功了！终于完成了！\\n“治愈熏香”做出来了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "“治愈熏香”……\\n噢噢！真的吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "刚才终于成型了。\\n这都是多亏之前采的香草。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "哈哈哈！太好了，加斯特！\\n你的熏香会拯救众多生命！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "不，现在高兴还太早了。\\n虽然理论上已经没问题，\\n但还需要长期的临床试验。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "为了确保能治好病，\\n必须反复验证确认疗效才行。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "加斯特，你在这里啊。\\n有人找你哦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "有人找我？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "你是之前森林里迷路的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "熏香大哥哥！\\n快救救奶奶！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "怎么了？出什么事了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "奶奶的病情加重了，\\n看上去非常痛苦！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "她一直在呻吟，这样下去的话\\n奶奶会……呜呜呜！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "那位老奶奶病重了吗。\\n可我能做的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "加斯特，\\n试试你的“治愈熏香”吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "我说过了……\\n熏香的功效还不确定。\\n而且说不定会有副作用……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "那也不一定就会失败呀。\\n而且按这孩子的说法，\\n这样下去情况可不妙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "既然这样，干脆死马当活马医。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "这……也许没错。\\n但万一没有效果……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "一到紧要关头就变得小心谨慎，\\n你还是老样子呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "但是加斯特，你是为了什么\\n才做出“治愈熏香”的？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "我做出“治愈熏香”的理由……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "那是因为……想要治愈那些\\n像祖父那样饱受病魔折磨的人。还有……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "为了不再看到\\n像过去的我一样悲痛万分的神情……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "那就别畏畏缩缩，\\n赶紧行动啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "是啊……\\n现在这里就有个悲痛万分的孩子。\\n既然如此……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "我们赶紧出发吧，卢卡！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "老奶奶，您感觉怎么样？有好点吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "祖母",
            "context": "啊……闻到这股香气，\\n感觉呼吸通畅多了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "真令人吃惊！村里的医生\\n都已经放弃治疗了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "奶奶，还难受吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "祖母",
            "context": "已经没事了，让你们担心了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "加斯特！\\n“治愈熏香”效果绝伦嘛！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "是啊。\\n看来效果比想象中稳定……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "理论上来说，只要每天都闻熏香，\\n疾病总有一天会痊愈。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "真的吗！？\\n那奶奶以后就能外出了。太好了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "那个，真不知道\\n要如何感谢你们才好……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "别放在心上！\\n帮助他人是理所当然的！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "谁让你回答了，真是的……呵呵。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "我留一些熏香在这里，\\n如果不够了，\\n随时可以来圣城找我。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "熏香大哥哥！谢谢你！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "你爷爷也一定很高兴。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "是这样就好了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "当天晚上，两人为研究的圆满成功\\n进行了小小的庆祝。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "几天后……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "加斯特，\\n这次你又在研究什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "我要给“治愈熏香”\\n增加各种不同的种类。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "柑橘系、鲜花系……\\n为了让大家能选择自己喜欢的香味。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "哈哈，你还真是热衷研究啊～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "加斯特，之前来的那个女孩\\n和她母亲一起过来了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "是那对母女啊。\\n应该是熏香用完了吧。我这就去。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "熏香大哥哥们……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "让你们久等了。\\n“治愈熏香”的存货……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "不，我们不是为那个来的。\\n母亲……前几天去世了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "诶！？你说什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "多亏了“治愈熏香”，\\n母亲一度恢复到了\\n能和这孩子外出的程度。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "但还是没能彻底痊愈……\\n前几天早上，在睡梦中……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "怎么会……我的熏香，\\n还是没能救活她吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "不，并不是这样。\\n多亏了你，\\n母亲最后走得很安详。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "如果没有你的熏香，\\n她一定会走得很痛苦吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "所以我们今天是来道谢的。\\n真的非常感谢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "大哥哥，送你花。\\n这是我和奶奶一起采的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "奶奶好久没有外出了，\\n所以看起来特别幸福。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "我也是。\\n非常开心！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "这样啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "你也睡不着吗，加斯特。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "卢卡……是啊，一闭上眼，\\n眼前就浮现出那孩子的笑容。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "接受现实向前看，\\n但还是有些落寞的那个笑容……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "加斯特……你的熏香\\n绝对不是失败的产物。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "正是因为你的熏香，\\n那孩子和奶奶最后才能笑着道别。\\n所以……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "话说在前头，我不需要安慰。\\n在这里消沉可就大错特错了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "是啊，就借着这股劲继续努力吧。\\n不过呢……加斯特。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "要继续努力的话，\\n现在就别太勉强自己。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "说出你的真心话吧。不然会变得\\n和之前一样，整个人都硬邦邦的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0075",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "真心话吗。说实话……\\n我很遗憾没能救活那位老奶奶。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0076",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "而且，我本不想让那孩子\\n露出那种落寞的笑容。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0077",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "进一步说，我其实至今仍对\\n没能替祖父做些什么心有不甘。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0078",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "祖父去世的那天，\\n我决定不再哭泣。\\n明明已经决定了！可是！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0079",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "卢卡，我还……\\n没能拯救希望拯救之人……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0080",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "这样的自己真是太没用了……\\n我……我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0081",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "是啊……虽然你很努力，\\n但还没有达成夙愿。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0082",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "那就在这里发誓吧。\\n我帮你做个见证。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0083",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "发誓……我……\\n我要完成能治愈疾病的熏香！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0084",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "这不是我想实现的梦想！\\n而是必须达成的目标！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0085",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "没错，那不是梦想而是目标。\\n如果遇到挫折……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110318_01_04_0086",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "我会鞭策你的。所以，加斯特，\\n你就放心向前冲吧。",
